Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:39.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}坦露自己的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:44.09,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}任凭此身沉浮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你握紧冰冷的十指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}脸上是悲切的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:53.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我无言以对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:56.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}只有视野渐渐模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不需言语粉饰
