Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff1,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见 你会记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.09,0:00:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕会就这样习惯了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.91,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得自己好像会变成别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家其实都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始终不变这种事或许没有人能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们确实活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.25,0:00:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远见…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会记得你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.97,0:00:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在改变主意还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 到外面的世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就…
